name: Barrios con  un centro de salud y o hospital
query:
SELECT 
    ef.efector AS "Nombre efector", 
    ef.dirección AS "Dirección", 
    ef.latitud AS "Latitud", 
    ef.longitud AS "Longitud", 
    ef.distrito AS "Distrito", 
    ef.barrio AS "Barrio", 
    ef.lineas_TUP AS "Líneas de Colectivo", 
    ef.tipo_efector AS "Tipo de efector"
FROM 
    tabEfector ef
WHERE 
    ef.barrio IN (
        SELECT efe.barrio
        FROM tabEfector efe
        GROUP BY efe.barrio
        HAVING COUNT(efe.barrio) = 1
    )
ORDER BY 
    ef.barrio;
report_name: Barrios con  un centro de salud y o hospital
